import numpy as np
data = pd.DataFrame({'  ..':[3865890,4553244,5221417,6181534,6950737,7827957,9520654,
                                          10035651,10848419,12249735,12981247,13852945],
                    'USD/RUB':[28.3,27.17,25.58,24.86,31.83,30.36,29.39,31.08,31.85,38.61,61.07,66.08],
                        })
data.index = range(2005,2017)
plt.figure(figsize = (10,6))
data['  . .'] = round(data['  ..']/data['USD/RUB'],2)
data['  . .'].plot(lw = 1,title = '     ""')
years = np.array([i for i in range(2005,2017)],dtype = np.int64)
plt.grid(True)
plt.scatter(years,data['  . .'].values,c = 'r')
plt.ylabel('Assets in mills $',color = 'r',fontsize = 15)
plt.xlabel('Year',color = 'b',fontsize = 15);
